Here’s my husband John donating plasma at the Mayo Clinic! People like John who've recovered from coronavirus have antibodies in their blood—which may help others fight the virus. If you have had Coronavirus you may be able to do the same. Get more info: https://t.co/7Le4RNaOk9 https://t.co/lNX2vyRTgu,2020-04-27 16:17:58,Twitter Web App,1195,10703,corona; 
